I"I<h1 id="in-a-nutshell">In a nutshell</h1>

<p class="nutshell">Set ambitious goals and commit to them with passion. Others will see
this commitment and be prepared to follow you. Strive for growth and
don’t let fear hold you back.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Set ambitious goals for your life/projects
    <ul>
      <li>Whilst these might be unrealistic, they shift the bar of your
expectations and your effort</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Commit to your goals with passion
    <ul>
      <li>To succeed you have to be obsessed with your goals; they must
dominate your thoughts and become your mission</li>
      <li>When others see how obsessed and committed you are, they will be
prepared to follow you on your journey to realise your wildly
ambitious goals</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Strive for growth; don’t let fear hold you back</li>
</ol>
